Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs28\1c&0x0000B2\3c&0x39E2E5\bord1\b1\pos(192,250)}飞出个未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\1c&0x5AE5E6\b1\bord0}失落的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息 各位\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Good news everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我把行星快递卖给老妈了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I've sold Planet Express to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 你戴着这顶怪里怪气的帽子干嘛\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Also, why are you wearing that funky hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这个啊 毫无理由\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh! This? No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 很可疑 十分的可疑\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}That was odd. Mighty odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你脑子短路了吗 教授\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Are you off our net, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能把公司卖给老妈\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}How could you sell the company to Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,迫不得已啊 我们一直在亏钱\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I had to. We've been losing money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我这个每次都动用一大艘飞船\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Perhaps my strategy of using a giant spaceship
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,来运送一个小包裹的策略\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}deliver one package at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有我想的那么明智\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}wasn't as clever as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 你们仨从来都不收钱\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Plus, you three never actually charged anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 真抱歉  - 不好意思\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeah, sorry about that.  - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这太令人弯心了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Aww, this bends!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 别大惊小怪 又不是世界末日要来了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, fuff. It's not like this is the end of the world as we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,世界末日要来了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}This is the end of the world as we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有没有注意到\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Has anyone never noticed that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱打开电视的时机总是这么巧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Fry always seems to turn on the TV at just the right moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在收购了行星快递后\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}With the recent purchase of Planet Express,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,邪恶的企业家"老妈"\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}evil entrepeneur Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在获得了超过50％的地球拥有权\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}now owns over 50% of the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这使她成为了地球的至高首领\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}making her its supreme ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,顶着舆论的压力\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}At the risk of editorializing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,本记者表示 很高兴看到人类这个可悲物种被占领\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}this reporter applaudes the demise of the pathetic human species.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的情况十分严峻\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The situation is indeed grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.04,0:02:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我们转接到老妈的现场讲话\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}We go now to a live statement from Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 别担心 亲爱的孩子们\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Ooh, don't worry dearies,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一造成的变化就是\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The only change I'm making is that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"地球母亲"现在得叫做"地球老妈"了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Mother Earth will now be called Mom Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 还挺萌的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Aww, that's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 你们现在全都是我的奴隶了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Also, you're all my slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚宵禁之前没有来报到的人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And anyone who doesn't report for duty before curfew tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,将被我的死亡机器人军团消灭\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}will be blasted by Hoverbot Death Troopers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,事后看来 也许确实不该把行星快递卖给她\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}In hindsight, maybe I shouldn't have sold her Planet Express.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是白内障蒙蔽了我\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Must be my hind cataracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 地球已经不安全了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Well, the Earth isn't safe anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,作为船长 我提议我们赶快逃离这里\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}As captain, I propose we get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命 老姐\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Amen, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,全员登船\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}To the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 飞船基本上报废了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, no, the ship's all wind up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会做出这种事情\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Who could have done such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不是我 我发誓\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}It wasn't me this time, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谁干的不要紧 我们必须赶快把船修好\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}No matter. We need to repair the ship and we need to do it fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,丽拉  你赶快去捣鼓一下控制台\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Leela, you start banging on the control panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这就去\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,本德 你负责把飞船掰回原样\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Bender, you'll have to bend the ship back into shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 为什么那些掰活儿总是交给我呢\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Man, how come I always have to do all the bending around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还有弗莱 你…呃…\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And, Fry, you... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你究竟会做些什么\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}what exactly do you know how to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我会用打嗝念字母表\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I can burp the alphabet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A B D
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不 等等\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你一个任务吧 弗莱\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I've got a mission for you, Fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,去找一把锤子\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Find a hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 长官\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 发生了什么\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh... what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你被两吨杂物压扁了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You were crushed under two tons of debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你死了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太搞笑了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}It was so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你得在现场看见才好笑\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I guess you had to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白 如果死在那里的是我 那这个我是谁\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I don't get it. If that's me dead over there, who am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个你也是你 多亏了我的最新发明\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You're also you, thanks to my latest invention...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,动画重绘仪\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...the Reanimator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,每当你死亡 它就会自动产生一个你的复制体\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Every time you die, it will automatically make an exact duplicate of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,根据你的 X光 DNA样本\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...based on your x- rays, a DNA sample...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和一些从你的网球鞋里刮下来的碎屑\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...and some scrapings from the inside of your tennis shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦 你什么时候发明的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Wow, when did you invent it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,大概一周以前\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}About a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,从那开始我就一直想杀了你来测试一下\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And I've been trying to kill you to test it ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 教授 这就是我用生命换来的锤子\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, professor, here's the hammer I died getting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哟哦 你留着这破玩意吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Wha...? Oh, you can keep that piece of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很可惜 还有一部分我无法修复\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Sadly, though, there was one part I was unable to repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别是暗物质引擎\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Not the Dark Matter Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,暗物质引擎\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The Dark Matter Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 倒霉\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Ah, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们不是有一个备用引擎吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But don't we have a backup engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经有\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们从来没有用过它 它一直在那儿备着\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But we never used it, it being backup and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我把它典当了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So I pawned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你把它典当了 为什么\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You pawned it? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,和每个美国人典当东西的原因一样\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}For the same reason everyone pawns everything in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为了买枪\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}To get a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 弗莱 去典当铺把我们的引擎弄回来\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Okey-dokey, Fry, go to the pawnshop and get back our engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但外面还在宵禁呢\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But there's a curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡机器人军团正在街头巡逻着\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hoverbot Death Troopers are roaming the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就只能走下水道了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Then you'll have to take the sewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但下水道有变种人啊\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But what about the Sewer Mutants?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是给了你一把枪吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I gave you a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你还想要什么 一件花衣服吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}What do you want, a flowered dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 别再窝在这儿了 快行动起来\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Now, stop being a wussy and get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿着这个套管显胖吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Does this casing make me look fat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,别再问我这些了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Stop asking me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我本应喜欢机器女人 但有时候\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I know I'm supposed to like robot women, but sometimes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢人类女人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You like human women?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不 机器男人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}No, robot men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,当我有"鸡行器"可以用的时候\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Why use my own legs like an idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,何必要傻兮兮的自己走路呢\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}when I can use a Chicken walker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,弗莱 你拿到引擎了 干得好\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Fry, you have the engine. Great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你让所有人都惊讶了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You surprised us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这次是惊喜不是惊吓\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And pleasantly this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 弗莱很棒\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeah, Fry's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我们开动吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Now, let's roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,副驾驶归我\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 引擎已就位\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}There. The engine's in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个给我很多条命的玩意儿也装备好了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And we've got that gizmo that gives me more lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,准备起飞\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Prepare for liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了 蓝色的大笨球\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Farewell, big blue ball of idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙 准备好被征服吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Universe, prepare to be taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你推出 "地球飞船"\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I give you Spaceship Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有一艘飞船正在飞离地球 老妈\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}A ship appears to be leaving the planet, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 让我看看\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}What? Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就在雷达显示屏上\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}It's right here on the radar screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,混帐 拉里\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Damn it, Larry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,雷达已经淘汰了几个世纪了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Radar's been obsolete for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,使用立体影像系统\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Use the stereopticon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我活该 谢谢\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I deserved that. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,行星快递的飞船\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The Planet Express ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 他们想逃跑是吗 没关系\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So they're trying to escape, eh? No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只需要像抓小猫一样把他们一网打尽\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}We'll just have to hunt them down like common kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,加大能量\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}More power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 老妈 长官\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Aye, aye, Mom, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,加大 加大 用力拉 你这个我的儿子\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}More, more. Pull harder, you son of a me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我嘞个妖孽的屁股蛋哟\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Sweet butt crust on a cracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会想到这个悲惨的小星球会重成这样\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Who'd have thought this miserable little planet would be so heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沃尔特就能\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Uh, Walt would.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你好大的胆子 沃尔特\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}How dare you, Walt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到萨尔回收站\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Welcomes to Sal's salvage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以为你们做什么\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}What can I do's youse for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一个宇宙飞船引擎 没什么特别的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I need a spaceship engine. Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 只不过 它必须有足够的力量来移动地球\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Well, except it has to be powerful enough to move the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,地球 老天爷啊\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The Earth? Holy Jesuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要这么做 你将需要一个暗物质引擎\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}For that, you're gonna needs a Dark Matter Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而且得是很大型的才行\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And a big ones at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,报酬不用担心 因为我很快就会占领全宇宙\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Money's no object, as I will soon be taking over the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你有所耳闻\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Perhaps you've heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 暗物质发动机\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hmm. A Dark Matter Engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须找到它的发明者\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You're gonna have to finds the guy who inventeds it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,休伯特·法斯沃斯\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hubert Farnsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,行星快递的那只老山羊\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}That old goat from Planet Express?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但他刚刚逃走了 那个爱妈的 一无是处的老\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But he just got away, that mother-loving, no good piece of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要担心 我有很多一个主意\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Don't worrys. I gots an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 一个很多主意\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I mean, an ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息 我给重绘仪编写了程序\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Good news. I've programmed the Reanimator...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,使它对本德也能起作用了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...to work for Bender as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在我可以像弗莱一样死而复生了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So now I can die and come back to life like Fry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我这辈子最开心的一天\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}This is the happiest day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它们困在吸引光束里了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I gots them in the suck beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呐\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, my. Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天呐 天呐 天呐\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, my, oh, my, oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都保持冷静\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Everyone just remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要死了 大难临头各自飞吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}We're gonna die. It's every robot for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那个机器人似乎正在逃跑\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Um, that robot appears to be escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 逃向注定的死亡\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yes, escaping to certain death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我完蛋了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Well, I'm boned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了 宝贝\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I'm back, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,本德 你真是一个机械奇迹\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Bender, you mechanical marvel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你在吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 什么\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在说话 是上帝吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Who said that? Is it God?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 虽然我是有他这么老了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}No, though I'm as old as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你好教授 你在我的脑袋里做什么\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh. Hey, professor, what are you doing inside my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在使用你的内置广播进行通话 你好\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I'm transmitting over your internal radio. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的飞船还困在吸引光束里\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Our ship is still trapped in the suck ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你找到光束的发射源 并把它关掉\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}We need you to find the source of the beam and disable it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这对本德我有什么好处\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}What's in it for me, Bender?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 这个…不 我们会营救你\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Uh, well... No. We'll rescue you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,并带你离开这个被遗弃的小行星\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...take you with us off this God-forsaken asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没门\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}No deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我这儿有一盒杂志\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I've got a box of magazines...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有很多女机器人的写真\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...with fembot centerfolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 完毕并出发\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Roger that. Over and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的机器人 你还没有见识到我的绝招\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Cursed robot. You haven't seen the last of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你死了 否则别让我逮到你 虽然你已经死了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Unless you die before I see you again, in which case you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好 本德\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Good work, Bender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你救我们脱离了老妈邪恶的关节炎触发器\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You saved us from Mom's evil arthritic clutches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 很好 很好 很好\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeah, good. Good, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那么现在呢 教授呢\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So, what now, professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你要发明出什么拯救世界的东西吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Are you gonna invent something that saves the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你通常都是这么做的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}That's what you usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 我的发明功力还没有那么厉害\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Alas, I'm not that skilled an inventor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道一个人能做到的人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But I know someone who is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我的导师和前研究生顾问 阿多维\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}My mentor and former graduate adviser, Adoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他住在波加达星球\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}He lives here on the planet Bogad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但那在宇宙中最遥远的角落\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But that's in the furthest corner of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们剩余的的暗物质燃料\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And we don't have enough dark matter fuel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至不够我们驶出太阳系\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...to get out of the solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那么看来你得去找一些燃料来了 丽拉\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Then I guess you'll have to find some, Leela.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们无路可逃了 鼻涕脑袋\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The jig is up, snot heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们才从你那里逃走\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But we just got away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 当初我在小行星上的时候 \N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hmm. I probably should have disabled their ship or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,也许应该把他们的船之类的也关掉\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...when I was down on that asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 吃一堑长一智\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Well, live and learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要什么 老妈\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}What do you want, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要你的暗物质引擎的设计图\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I've come for the blueprints to your Dark Matter Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那你可不走运了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Well, you're out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的蓝图只存在于我的大脑里\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The only blueprints are here in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 好吧 那我就要你的头了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Ugh. Fine. Then we'll take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的部分是幻影痔疮\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The worst part is the phantom hemorrhoids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为我的斩首报仇\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Avenge my decapitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是时候除掉那些残余的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Now to get rid of the rest of those
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,行星快递的走狗了 以绝后患\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Planet Express jerk-bots once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 一切都很顺利\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}All right. Everything worked out fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 我们正在直接冲向太阳\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, no, we're heading straight into the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在冲向太阳\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}We're heading into the sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不算是我最好的着陆 大家还好吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Not my best landing. Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我还好\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeah, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,幸运的是 我摔在了某个柔软的东西上\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Fortunately, I landed on something soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很好 告诉我们超重的机器人朋友 不用谢\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I'm fine too. No thanks to our chubby robot friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,至少飞船还能运行\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}At least the ship is operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该能够轻松离开这里\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}We should be able to get out of here easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我们耗尽了暗物质燃料\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Unless we're out of dark matter fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们确实耗尽了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Which we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到太阳城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不欢迎游客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 过来看看\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Whoa. Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 弗莱 你不应该直视太阳\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Be careful, Fry. You're not supposed to look directly at the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,问候 你们来自其他星球的外星人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Greeting, you aliens from other planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 哦 好的 我来搞定\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}What? Oh, okay, fine. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:16:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 带我们去见你的领导\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Uh, take us to your leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是太阳王 Ra-Ra\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I am Ra-Ra the Sun King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一般来说 这意味着我就是领导\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}but we have little coup d'etat recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但最近我们有点小小的政变\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}but we have little coup d'etat recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是共产主义的无神论者吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Was it godless communists?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是神 强大的 强大的太阳神\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}No, it was God. Mighty, mighty Sun God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,显然 他最近迷上了他的信徒的肉味\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Apparently, him develop taste for flesh of own worshippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳人民非常害怕\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Sun people so afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们甚至不敢踏出自家的太阳门\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}they not even set foot on own sun porches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,司空见惯了 总有人害怕这个神那个神的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Big whoop. Everyone's afraid of some god or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 我们更害怕不死战士的军队\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Actually, we more afraid of army of undead warriors...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳神用受难者的骨头制造出来的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...Sun God create from bones of victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这个还差不多\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, those will get you, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也许如果你们能想办法进入密封的寺庙\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Perhaps if you find way into sealed temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就可以击败太阳神 拯救太阳人民\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...you can defeat Sun God and save Sun people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我确实关心你们差劲的人民 和劣质的寺庙\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Gee, I really care about your lame people and your crummy temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但 这事儿还是算了吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...but we're gonna have to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会得到丰厚的回报\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You'd be handsomely rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,算我一个\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 忠实的朋友 你们有没有暗物质\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So, kemosabe, you got any dark matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是我们的主要出口产品\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}It our chief export.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那就这么定了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Then you've got yourself a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 你们两个要去哪儿\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hey, where are you two going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 丽拉 很乐意帮你拯救太阳 但我太容易烧着\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Sorry, Leela, I'd love to help you save the sun, but I burn easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:17:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而我太容易烧化 但帮我留着我的那份报酬\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And I melt easily. But save me my share of the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好大一台烤面包机\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}That big toaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有大事要发生\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Something's about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那感觉深入骨髓\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I can feel it in my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,说得不错\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你不会觉得上帝也会受伤吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Huh. You wouldn't think a god could be mortally wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,被你发现了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You found me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实并不是一个神\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I'm not really a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是一个普普通通的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I'm just an ordinary
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,永恒且无所不知的超智能生命体而已\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}eternal, omniscient, super-intelligent being.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你为什么允许那些人被杀害\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So why did you allow all those people to be killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是为了他们的骨头\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}For their bones, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我用来创建我的骨器人军队\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Which I use to create my army of bone-bots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,骨器人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Bone-bots?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 正常人都用全属来造他们的机器人军队\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You know, normal people make their robot armies out of metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 但我的方式更邪恶\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yes, but my way is more evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 啊\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Whoa! Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,邪恶的太阳神已经走了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Evil Sun God is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 怪异的独眼女人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Thank you, weird, one-eyed woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你拯救了我们的行星\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You save our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是恒星 实际上\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Star, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 现在 给你们的奖励\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Whatever. And now for reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能装满整个油箱的暗物质\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Full tank worth dark matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好哎 宝贝\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, yeah, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快加满油 然后离开这个糟糕的鬼地方吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Let's fuel up and ditch this awful sty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 无意冒犯\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Uh, no offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意 但首先 你们一定要来到寺庙和我们庆祝一番\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}None taken. But first, you must come to temple and celebrate with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,寺庙  - 是的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The temple? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,珍贵的寺庙 所有太阳生命的圣地\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Cherished temple. Sacred center of all life on sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 哈哈哈\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Uh... Ha-ha-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很想留下 但是 呃\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}We'd love to stay, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有…事情\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}we've got a, uh, thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 事情\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧撤\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Cheese it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真是些好人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Them nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我亲爱的教授脑袋\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Ah. My dear professor's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有了你的大脑和我的邪恶\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}with your brains and my evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我将很快就能称霸宇宙\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...I shall soon take over the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不会得逞的 老妈\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You'll never get away with it, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但我已经把地球变成了一艘巨大的战舰\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But I've turned the planet Earth into a gigantic warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪 这样的话 看来你确实很有可能得逞\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Ooh, my. In that case, you probably will get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哟\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好热 哦 天呐 我的头 哦 哦\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}It's hot! Oh, God, my head! Ooh... ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,疼 疼\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Pain, pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是波加达\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So this is Bogad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 很阴森 是吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Whoa, Creepy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 还很丑\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeah, and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法想象在这里我们会发现什么\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I can't imagine what kind of disgusting,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,令人恶心的污秽的生物\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}foul creatures we'll find here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伊博格医生 你在这里做什么\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Dr. Zoidberg? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,制做浮雕\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Making a cameo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你们 我的朋友们 和那个机器人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}It's so nice to see you, my friends and the robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这实在是不太可能\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}This is so unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 那个鬼东西是什么\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hey, what's that kajigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我不知道\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Mm. I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但从它的体形和长长的舌头判断\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But judging by its scales and long tongue...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢说这是一匹马\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...I'd say it's a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,叽哩呱啦 哟呵\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Giddyup! Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一个牛仔\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I'm a cowboy, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定就是这里了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}This must be the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你是阿多维吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Um, are you Adoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,阿多维 我已经很久没有听过这个名字了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Adoy? I haven't heard that name in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 就是我\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeah, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 好的 我们是教授派来的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Uh okay. We were sent here by the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我记得那位教授\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Ah. I remember the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了 那时候 我才是那个叫做教授的人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Of course, back then, I was the one called the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我们说的是哪个教授\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Wait, who are we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:21:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 倒霉\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,休伯特·法斯沃斯教授\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Professor Hubert Farnsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没听说过这人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Never heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我这个亲爱的老信徒需要我做什么呢\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So, what can I do for my dear old protege.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你也许能够帮助我们\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}He said you might be able to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,长话短说 老妈切下了他的脑袋\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Long story short, Mom cut off his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,现在她正在试图称霸宇宙\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...and now she's trying to take over the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 好可怕 真可怕 太可怕了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh. Terrible, terrible, terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在我们也做不了什么了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But there's nothing we can do about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.09,0:22:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 谢谢你们来看望我\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So it's a good thing you came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个家伙一点用都没有\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}This guy's not making any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以杀了他吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Can I kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的最新发明 时间隧道仪\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}This is my latest invention, the Time Tunneler.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有了它 你可以穿越到过去\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}With it, you can travel back in time and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在她变得势不可挡之前阻止她\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...stop Mom before she became unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,或者去赌马 保证能赢很多钱\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Or bet on horses I know are gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了 衰货们\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So long, suckers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 该死 我还在这里\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Ah, man, I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要先给它充电 阿多维\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You need to charge it first, Adoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,发电机在那边\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The power generator is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要去到那里 你们必须\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You can get to it along
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,穿过这条充满流沙的危险道路\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}this dangerous path, laden with quicksand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.13,0:22:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我知道\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I know, I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那里确实不是一个建造发电机的好地方\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}it was a terrible place to build the generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 行了吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I'm sorry. Give me a break here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但这台时光机有一个手柄 它不管用吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But the time machine has a hand crank. Doesn't that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 差不多吧 如果你把手柄转到两分钟的地方\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Uh, sort of. If you turn the handle for two minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它就会把宇宙送回到两分钟之前\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...it'll send the universe two minutes back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 它会回到我们转动手柄之前 好哟\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So it gets us back to when we started turning the handle? Yippee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不 等等 要拿到发电机 我们可能只需要这样做\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}No, wait. That might be all we need to get to the generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们中有人足够快的话\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}If one of us is fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.78,0:23:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 又一个危险的任务\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Great, another dangerous mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这次轮到哪个倒霉蛋\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Who's the sucker this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伊博格医生\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Dr. Zoidberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好哎 我是英雄\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hooray, I'm the hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好哎 我们什么事情都不用做\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hooray, we don't have to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 佐伊博格 一旦我开始开始转动\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Okay, Zoidberg, once I start cranking...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你只有两分钟的时间赶回到我的视线之内\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...you've got two minutes to get to where I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,否则 我就当你已经被杀了 并倒转时间\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Otherwise, I'll assume you've been killed and rewind time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被杀了 嗯\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Killed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是医生 但我听得出来那会很痛苦\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I'm no doctor, but that sounds painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是的 相信我\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, it is. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运 怪物诱饵\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Good luck, monster bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.48,0:24:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伊博格化险为夷\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Zoidberg makes it to safety...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,人们高兴得沸腾了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...and the crowd goes wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.31,0:24:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,佐伊博格拉动杠杆\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Zoidberg pulls the lever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.68,0:24:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,时间隧道仪起作用了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The Time Tunneler is working.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.85,0:24:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒优极了 现在我们可以回到过去对付老妈了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Fantabulistic. Now we can go back in time and fight Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.69,0:24:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,并救回教授\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And save the professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.07,0:24:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好好好 随便吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.60,0:24:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 英雄们\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Goodbye, heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.32,0:24:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你们是谁 但我永远不会忘记你们的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I'll never forget you, whoever you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.18,0:25:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我现在要做什么 伙计们\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}So, what should I do now, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.36,0:25:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗 朋友们\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hello? Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.92,0:25:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.20,0:25:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&0xFFFFFF}一周之前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.86,0:25:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要死了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.41,0:25:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么大不了的 我们一整天都在死\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}What's the big deal? We've been dying all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.05,0:25:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们比平时更加失控\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}We're even more out of control than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.08,0:25:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好颠簸的着陆\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Prepare for crappy landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.11,0:25:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,至少现在我们知道我们的飞船是谁毁掉的了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Well, at least now we know who trashed our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.36,0:25:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 已经九点了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, no, it's already 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.37,0:25:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们还想阻止老妈买下行星快递的话\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}If we wanna stop Mom from having bought Planet Express in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.05,0:25:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最好抓紧时间了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}we better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.01,0:25:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,到船上去\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}To the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.70,0:25:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 如果我了解时间悖论的话\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Now, if I understand time paradoxes,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.51,0:25:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该开走好的飞船\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}we're supposed to take the good ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.53,0:25:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把坏的飞船留给原来的我们 对吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...and leave the bad ship behind for the original us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.11,0:25:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,坏的留下\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The bad behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.12,0:25:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一遍\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Say again?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.96,0:25:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 进去就是了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh. Just get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.74,0:26:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦你在这里签了名 行星快递就是我的了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}As soon as you sign here, Planet Express will be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.06,0:26:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了什么搞笑的事吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Did I do something funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.08,0:26:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不 对不起\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}No. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.97,0:26:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该等你签完字之后再发出邪恶的笑声\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I should save my evil laugh till after you've signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.44,0:26:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.41,0:26:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要签 教授 我们来自未来\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Don't sign it, professor. We came from the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.77,0:26:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个圈套\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}It's a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.64,0:26:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啥\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.81,0:26:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦老妈得到了行星快递 她就会占领地球\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Once Mom gets Planet Express, she's gonna take over the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.19,0:26:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她会把地球改造成一个巨大的太空船\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And then she's gonna turn it into a giant spaceship...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.53,0:26:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然后称霸宇宙\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...and take over the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.12,0:26:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哎哟喂 那真是太酷了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Man, that was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.84,0:26:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,地球就像这样\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Earth is all:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.43,0:26:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,其他行星就像这样\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And the other planets are like:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.33,0:26:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真滑稽\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}How droll.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.37,0:26:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以跟你们三个说句话吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Could I talk to you three over here for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.08,0:27:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你往左边一点点\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}A little to your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.92,0:27:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.16,0:27:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,毁灭者退出打靶练习模式\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Destructor exiting target-practice mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.49,0:27:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,毁灭者启动"杀光所有人类"模式\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Destructor initiating kill-all-humans mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.80,0:27:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我至死也一直坚持做我自己\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}And so I die the way I lived:
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.77,0:27:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一个巨型机器人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}As a giant robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.10,0:27:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.99,0:27:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,打得好 弗莱\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Nice shooting, Fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.57,0:27:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么浪费了一个邪恶机器人\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Way to waste that evil robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.39,0:27:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 就因为一个机器人想要杀人 他就一定是邪恶的吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, so just because a robot wants to kill humans, he must be evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.01,0:27:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你的偏见真重 丽拉\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}That is so prejudiced, Leela.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.57,0:27:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他刚刚也想杀了你 本德\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}He wanted to kill you too, Bender.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.57,0:27:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 这个…\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.20,0:27:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你闭嘴\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.35,0:28:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 重绘仪\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, no, the Reanimator.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.77,0:28:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,倒霉 从现在起 我们必须小心行事 别随便死了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Bummer. We'll just have to be careful not to die from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.41,0:28:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你非要乌鸦嘴\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You had to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.87,0:28:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 该死 老妈 只有我才能杀死我的船员\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Ooh, damn it, Mom. No one kills my crew except for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.33,0:28:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你受死吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You're going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.33,0:28:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 得了吧 你是不会打女人的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, please. You wouldn't hit a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.11,0:28:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我想你是对的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.13,0:28:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我可以这样做\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Though I would do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.00,0:28:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿呀\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.70,0:28:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你打伤了我的髋关节\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You broke my hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.68,0:28:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.10,0:28:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你想得到行星快递 从而称霸宇宙是吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You wanted Planet Express so you could take over the universe, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.73,0:28:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想现在你的邪恶计划已经被挫败了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Well, I guess your evil plan is foiled now...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.85,0:28:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,全靠我穿越时空的船员\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...thanks to my time-traveling crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.22,0:29:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你必须把行星快递卖给我\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}But you have to sell Planet Express to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.81,0:29:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你的船员说过它已经发生了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Your crew said it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.69,0:29:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人可以改变时间的连续性\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}...and no one can alter the continuum of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.80,0:29:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 是吗 瞧我的\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh, yeah? Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.24,0:29:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,交易取消\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}The deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.54,0:29:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 好吧\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh. Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.81,0:29:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我附赠这顶帽子给你呢\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}How about if I throw in this hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.51,0:29:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.83,0:29:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息 各位\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Good news, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.49,0:29:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我把行星快递卖给老妈了\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I've sold Planet Express to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.41,0:29:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你看看这些个名字\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Oh. Look at all the names.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.01,0:29:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 确实是好多名字啊\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Yeah, it's a lot of names...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.58,0:29:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你不也希望自己的贡献受到致谢吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}... but wouldn't you want credit for something you did?
